These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, 7up
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, tulip, sunflower
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who growssunflower is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Beverage   | juice     | fanta | 7up |
| Flower   | sunflower  | marigold    | tulip      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, november, july
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, mechanic, journalist
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the mechanic##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person eating kale is the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the project-manager is between the fan of gospel and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | soul     | blues      |
| Birthday   | july  | november | february |
| Job           | journalist | project-manager     | mechanic       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, paramedic
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, board-games, sudoku
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, bus, snowmobile
1. the bartender is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person driving the car is between the paramedic and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the bus is the person eating kale##1
5. the person driving the car is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Job           | paramedic | bartender  | doctor   |
| Hobby   | collecting  | board-games    | sudoku |
| Transport           | snowmobile     | car | bus |

