.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, fuchsia, ebony
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
3 different games are played: domino, whist, snooker
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person who likes ebony is between the paramedic and the owner of the cat##2
4. the person who likes fuchsia is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Color    | blood-red       | ebony  | fuchsia   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| Game   | snooker | domino     | whist      |

