.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bluemaster, pall-mall
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, funk, gospel
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, manager, police-officer
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the scientist is between the fan of gospel and the pall-mall-smoker##2
3. the bolivar-smoker is the manager##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the scientist is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Cigar         | bolivar | bluemaster | pall-mall |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | funk       | disco       |
| Job           | manager     | scientist       | police-officer     |

