2. the person eating pumpkin is the scientist##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is between the person eating pineapple and the owner of the horse##2
4. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | pumpkin    |
| Job         | accountant | manager      | scientist |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | comedy     | horror        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

