.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, chestnut, grey
3 different games are played: bridge, canasta, go
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, western
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person playing canasta is between the person who likes grey and the person driving the car##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the person playing canasta is between the person playing go and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Color          | grey      | chestnut   | ebony |
| Game         | bridge | canasta | go |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

