1. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person drinking water##2
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | cola       | soy-milk      | water      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | ritmeester-climbing | chess      |
| Flower           | rose | daffodil     | dahlia |
| Cigar   | baccarat     | ritmeester          | oliveros       |

