3. the person eating pear is the wooden house##1
4. the person eating peach is the social-worker##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
