.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, milk
3 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, go
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival, art-deco
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, italian
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the italian##1
3. the indonesian is in the middle##1
4. the indonesian is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing domino##2
5. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
6. the person playing domino is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | milk     | hot-chocolate | coffee      |
| Game         | mah-jongg  | go       | domino |
| House   | art-deco   | gothic-revival         | ranch-style     |
| Nationality   | american | indonesian    | italian     |

