.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, golf, rowing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, soul, r&b
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, musical, sports
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, spanish
1. the person who's sport is golf is the fan of r&b##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the fan of soul and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Sport      | weightlifting | golf      | rowing            |
| Music-Genre           | dubstep | r&b | soul |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | sports        | horror         |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | australian    | spanish        |

