3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person eating garlic is the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1

