.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-15::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, cherry, potato
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
City: prague, paris, nizza
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, baseball, golf
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is between the fan of trance and the person traveling to nizza##2
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the fan of trance and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the fan of punk is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato  | cherry   | artichoke |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | punk     | classical |
| City   | prague | paris | nizza   |
| Sport     | golf   | baseball   | water-polo      |

