The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, comedy, horror
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, indian, mexican
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, tram
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the person watching horror movies is between the person driving the boat and the person watching western movies##2
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
4. the indian is the person driving the boat##1
5. the mexican is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby       | singing | gardening | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre         | western   | horror       | comedy        |
| Nationality       | mexican | nigerian   | indian         |
| Transport   | tram    | train     | boat         |

