.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk
House: futuristic, colonial, ranch-style
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, sudoku, cooking
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, ship, train
1. the colonial house is between the person driving the train and the futuristic house##2
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the fan of electronic is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is the fan of disco##1
5. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the futuristic house is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco  | folk     |
| House   | ranch-style    | colonial | futuristic |
| Hobby           | board-games        | cooking   | sudoku  |
| Transport     | train      | ship   | airplane |

