There 3 different types of food: peach, pear, nectarine
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, folk, salsa
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, mouse
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person eating nectarine is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person eating pear##1
5. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is chess and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing   | collecting   | chess |
| Food   | nectarine | pear   | peach     |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | d&b      | salsa    |
| Pet           | goldfish | hedgehog | mouse    |

