3. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person watching sports movies##2
4. the person who's sport is swimming is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is swimming##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| Movie-Genre         | drama   | musical | sports |
| Sport   | swimming        | cycling       | badminton      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

