.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
House: futuristic, craftsman, gothic-revival
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rabbit
3 different games are played: go, backgammon, chess
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person driving the car##1
3. the person playing backgammon is the person driving the car##1
4. the person playing go is the gothic-revival house##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the person driving the tram and the person playing backgammon##2
6. the person playing chess is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| House        | craftsman      | futuristic | gothic-revival |
| Pet         | goldfish     | rabbit    | dog        |
| Game       | backgammon | chess   | go   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 